features: USB AC Power Adapter Battery Charger Cord For Sony Cybershot DSC-W810
Brand New, High Quality AC Home/Wall Charger/Adapter ( Non-OEM ).
Package includes: 1 unit of battery charger adapter with USB cable.
Compatible with: Sony Camera Cybershot DSC-W810 / W810s / W810p / W810w
description: 100% brand new, high quality USB 2.0 charger data/lead cable (non-OEM).  This cable connects your camera to USB-ready PC/MAC/Laptop/Notebook or USB hub for data transferring.  2-in-1 feature: this cable can also transfer power.  High quality cable: Data transfer rates up to 480Mbps Foil and Braid Shielding to reduce EMI/RFI Interference Oxygen Free Copper Core with Environmental-friendly Recyclable Plastic  Twisted-Pair construction to ensure high-speed, error-free data transfer USB 1.0, 1.1 and 2.0 compatible  Heavy-duty cable. Light and easy to carry around: 4 FT long Compatible with: Sony Camera Cybershot DSC-W810 / W810s / W810p / W810w PLUS: Brand New, High Quality USB Charger. Input: 100-240 V Output: 5V, 1000mA max. With IC circuit inside and LED light indicator for preventing overcharging and for short circuit protection. Compact design, light and easy to carry. This charger combined with the above 2-in-1 cable results in an AC wall charger. In other words, this package can perform (1) AC wall power charging -- in-camera battery charging; (2) USB data transferring. Quantity in package/set : 1 USB charger data cable + 1 USB charger.
